$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGDMFGALL
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "DMFGALL" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [MFA1]
& As [MFA1]
Titled [MFA1] TIT
Return

$VISU_BOITE
Gosub INIT_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGDMFGALL
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "DMFGALL" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [MFA1]
& As [MFA1]
Titled [MFA1] TIT
Gosub AFF_BOITE
Return

